OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPortuguese parliament backs
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fassisted suicide bill      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Portugal's parliament has approved     
OL,6, legislation to allow medically assisted
OL,7, suicide in limited circumstances.      
OL,9,FOnce enacted, the bill would allow this
OL,10,Fform of euthanasia if an adult's wish  
OL,11,Fto die is "current and reiterated,     
OL,12,Fserious, free and informed".           
OL,14,FThe person must be "in a situation of  
OL,15,Fgreat intensity suffering, with        
OL,16,Fdefinitive injury of extreme gravity or
OL,17,Fserious and incurable disease".        
OL,19,FThe measure has parallels in only a    
OL,20,Fhandful of countries worldwide.        
